Dialogue: 0,0:02:33.54,0:02:37.61,OP-CH,,0,0,0,,{\blur5\fad(300,300)}沒有什麼比真相
Dialogue: 0,0:02:37.70,0:02:44.60,OP-CH,,0,0,0,,{\blur5\fad(300,300)}更加對人殘酷
