Dialogue: 0,0:03:28.65,0:03:29.40,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}咦
Dialogue: 0,0:03:29.74,0:03:30.62,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}友奈
Dialogue: 0,0:03:31.45,0:03:32.43,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}東鄉同學
Dialogue: 0,0:03:34.28,0:03:37.06,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}不是吧 難道說…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:40.05,0:03:40.74,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}姐姐
Dialogue: 0,0:03:40.74,0:03:41.47,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}樹
Dialogue: 0,0:03:41.58,0:03:44.44,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}太好了 姐姐你沒事
Dialogue: 0,0:03:44.44,0:03:46.27,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}那個…大家的樣子很奇怪
Dialogue: 0,0:03:46.27,0:03:47.02,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}於是…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:47.02,0:03:47.94,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}樹
Dialogue: 0,0:03:48.93,0:03:51.21,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}樹 聽我說
Dialogue: 0,0:03:51.84,0:03:53.21,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}我們…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:53.92,0:03:54.92,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}被選中了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:58.93,0:04:01.82,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}這種現象被稱為樹海化
Dialogue: 0,0:04:01.82,0:04:02.52,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}地震？
Dialogue: 0,0:04:02.52,0:04:03.51,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}時間停滯下來
Dialogue: 0,0:04:03.66,0:04:08.48,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}被選為勇者的我們被送往神樹大人所創造的結界之中
Dialogue: 0,0:04:09.91,0:04:15.04,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}大赦派遣來的風學姐將勇者適應值較高的少女收集起來
Dialogue: 0,0:04:15.25,0:04:16.51,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}創立了勇者社
Dialogue: 0,0:04:16.51,0:04:17.65,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}是人類的敵人
Dialogue: 0,0:04:17.65,0:04:23.24,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}勇者為了讓世界免受Vertex這一神秘生命體的襲擊而戰鬥
Dialogue: 0,0:04:25.42,0:04:29.63,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}一旦Vertex抵達神樹大人 世界就會毀滅
Dialogue: 0,0:04:30.32,0:04:35.95,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}為了阻止它 我們展現出戰鬥的意志 成為神樹大人的勇者
Dialogue: 0,0:04:37.24,0:04:41.93,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}世界說不定會毀滅 大家也面臨著危險
Dialogue: 0,0:04:42.23,0:04:45.32,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}而我卻沒能展現出意志
Dialogue: 0,0:04:45.32,0:04:46.44,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}友奈
Dialogue: 0,0:04:46.44,0:04:48.14,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}然而 友奈她…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:50.94,0:04:51.79,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}我不要那樣
Dialogue: 0,0:04:54.19,0:04:57.64,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}看著別人受到傷害 經歷苦難
Dialogue: 0,0:04:59.24,0:05:02.62,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}與其讓別人經歷這樣的痛苦
Dialogue: 0,0:05:05.21,0:05:08.69,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}不如由我來努力
Dialogue: 0,0:05:11.03,0:05:12.36,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}友奈
Dialogue: 0,0:05:12.58,0:05:17.49,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}勇者衝拳
Dialogue: 0,0:05:22.03,0:05:23.68,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}勇者社的活動內容是
Dialogue: 0,0:05:24.08,0:05:26.53,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}為了大家鼓起勇氣做好事
Dialogue: 0,0:05:27.33,0:05:32.00,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}我是讚州國中勇者社 結城友奈
Dialogue: 0,0:05:32.67,0:05:35.47,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}我來成為勇者
Dialogue: 0,0:05:36.93,0:05:38.36,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}沒跟你們說真是對不起
Dialogue: 0,0:05:38.98,0:05:43.60,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}那怎麼不早點把勇者社真正的意義告訴我們
Dialogue: 0,0:05:44.14,0:05:47.75,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}友奈和樹說不定會死的呀
Dialogue: 0,0:05:48.67,0:05:49.56,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}對不起
Dialogue: 0,0:05:49.80,0:05:52.31,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}但是就算勇者適應性再高
Dialogue: 0,0:05:52.45,0:05:54.63,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}哪個小隊會被神樹大人選中
Dialogue: 0,0:05:54.75,0:05:56.40,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}在敵人來之前是無法知道的
Dialogue: 0,0:05:57.05,0:05:59.19,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}因為這是涉及人類存亡的頭等大事
Dialogue: 0,0:06:00.21,0:06:04.46,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}一直瞞著我們…這麼重要的事嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:06:05.92,0:06:06.83,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}東鄉…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:07.83,0:06:10.85,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}要是只有我一個人無法變身
Dialogue: 0,0:06:11.25,0:06:13.32,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}就會成為勇者社的累贅
Dialogue: 0,0:06:14.71,0:06:16.80,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}對輸給恐懼的自己感到羞愧
Dialogue: 0,0:06:17.46,0:06:20.79,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}對風學姐說了過分的話
Dialogue: 0,0:06:21.52,0:06:22.77,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}但是我很高興
Dialogue: 0,0:06:22.89,0:06:26.87,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}因為正是由於適應性讓我與風學姐和樹相遇了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:28.20,0:06:30.26,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}是因為這適應性？
Dialogue: 0,0:06:30.52,0:06:31.16,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:06:32.41,0:06:34.09,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}以後也會很開心哦
Dialogue: 0,0:06:34.59,0:06:36.84,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}只是多了有點困難的任務而已
Dialogue: 0,0:06:38.70,0:06:39.65,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}是嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:06:39.85,0:06:40.82,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}也是啊
Dialogue: 0,0:06:41.93,0:06:45.13,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}我也很高興與大家相識
Dialogue: 0,0:06:46.26,0:06:48.80,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}保護這個世界是我們的使命
Dialogue: 0,0:06:49.57,0:06:53.54,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}倘若我也有保護我珍愛的朋友的力量
Dialogue: 0,0:06:56.47,0:06:57.43,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}不要
Dialogue: 0,0:06:57.73,0:07:02.52,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}不要欺負友奈
Dialogue: 0,0:07:08.17,0:07:09.70,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}東鄉同學…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:36.20,0:07:37.78,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}據風學姐所說
Dialogue: 0,0:07:38.03,0:07:41.14,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}只要打倒十二隻Vertex 我們的任務也就結束了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:41.83,0:07:47.36,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}而且大赦還派遣了經過特別訓練的夏凜加入我們
Dialogue: 0,0:07:48.25,0:07:51.00,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}一開始對勇者社持否定態度的夏凜
Dialogue: 0,0:07:51.27,0:07:53.43,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}也漸漸地敞開心扉
Dialogue: 0,0:07:54.39,0:07:58.48,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}大家度過著珍愛的日常 憧憬著夢想
Dialogue: 0,0:07:59.19,0:08:00.59,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}要保護好這一切
Dialogue: 0,0:08:05.68,0:08:06.98,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}剩下七隻
Dialogue: 0,0:08:08.05,0:08:09.96,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}怎麼全部都攻過來了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:11.64,0:08:13.79,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}真是最糟糕的襲擊模式
Dialogue: 0,0:08:14.53,0:08:16.69,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}出陣
Dialogue: 0,0:08:18.76,0:08:20.50,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}好 去殲滅
Dialogue: 0,0:08:20.50,0:08:21.68,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}我們也上
Dialogue: 0,0:08:21.68,0:08:22.32,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}是
Dialogue: 0,0:08:24.30,0:08:28.29,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}將積蓄的能量釋放出來 就是勇者的王牌「盛開」
Dialogue: 0,0:08:28.92,0:08:32.90,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}透過不斷地盛開 勇者的力量將得到增幅
Dialogue: 0,0:08:33.48,0:08:35.43,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}大赦是這樣說明的
Dialogue: 0,0:08:36.36,0:08:38.63,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}面對著剩下的七隻Vertex
Dialogue: 0,0:08:39.04,0:08:41.20,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}我們相繼地盛開
Dialogue: 0,0:08:44.42,0:08:45.47,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}「盛開」
Dialogue: 0,0:08:54.86,0:08:57.46,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}就是那裡
Dialogue: 0,0:09:01.36,0:09:02.87,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}大家幹得好
Dialogue: 0,0:09:03.07,0:09:06.32,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}為了慶祝勇者社大勝利 乾杯
Dialogue: 0,0:09:06.32,0:09:07.99,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}乾杯
Dialogue: 0,0:09:11.21,0:09:14.20,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}目標達成之後的果汁果然就是不一樣
Dialogue: 0,0:09:15.87,0:09:18.69,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}在那場戰鬥中經歷了盛開的人
Dialogue: 0,0:09:18.76,0:09:20.76,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}身體都出現了異常
Dialogue: 0,0:09:21.40,0:09:22.51,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}友奈是味覺
Dialogue: 0,0:09:23.25,0:09:24.68,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}風學姐是左眼
Dialogue: 0,0:09:25.79,0:09:27.12,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}樹是聲音
Dialogue: 0,0:09:28.18,0:09:29.41,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}我是左耳
Dialogue: 0,0:09:31.01,0:09:34.26,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}雖然大赦的醫生說應該馬上就會痊癒
Dialogue: 0,0:09:34.71,0:09:36.55,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}但卻完全沒有好轉的跡象
Dialogue: 0,0:09:37.28,0:09:41.63,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}然後 我知道了勇者系統的真相
Dialogue: 0,0:09:41.99,0:09:44.86,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}我一直在呼喚你呀 鷲鷲
Dialogue: 0,0:09:45.01,0:09:46.78,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}真是想死我了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:50.70,0:09:52.88,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}她的名字叫做乃木園子
Dialogue: 0,0:09:53.88,0:09:59.50,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}她用那悲傷的眼神緊盯著我 稱呼我為鷲鷲
Dialogue: 0,0:10:01.56,0:10:04.38,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}友奈經歷過「盛開」對吧
Dialogue: 0,0:10:05.46,0:10:08.96,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}一下開放 一下變強的那個
Dialogue: 0,0:10:10.20,0:10:11.85,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}對 經歷過
Dialogue: 0,0:10:12.54,0:10:14.45,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}我也經歷過
Dialogue: 0,0:10:14.64,0:10:19.08,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}你們覺得綻放盛開的花之後會怎樣
Dialogue: 0,0:10:19.76,0:10:25.12,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}盛開之後 身體應該有什麼部位會變得不方便的
Dialogue: 0,0:10:30.70,0:10:37.33,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}我覺得大赦的人們掩蓋這一系統也算是一種同情
Dialogue: 0,0:10:38.79,0:10:46.88,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}不過 我真的好想被好好告知這些事
Dialogue: 0,0:10:49.81,0:10:50.92,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}要是早知道會這樣
Dialogue: 0,0:10:51.54,0:10:59.15,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}就會更珍惜和朋友玩耍的機會了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:10.36,0:11:12.76,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}那個髮帶真適合你
Dialogue: 0,0:11:14.31,0:11:18.53,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}這條髮帶是非常重要的東西
Dialogue: 0,0:11:19.87,0:11:21.65,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}我只記得這些
Dialogue: 0,0:11:22.35,0:11:26.18,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}但是…對不起
Dialogue: 0,0:11:26.28,0:11:28.40,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}我想不起來
Dialogue: 0,0:11:29.47,0:11:31.49,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}沒辦法呀
Dialogue: 0,0:11:39.58,0:11:40.80,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}怎麼了 東鄉
Dialogue: 0,0:11:41.08,0:11:42.14,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}突然叫我們過來
Dialogue: 0,0:11:44.38,0:11:48.04,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}我有東西想給風學姐和友奈看看
Dialogue: 0,0:11:49.36,0:11:50.96,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}東…東鄉同學
Dialogue: 0,0:11:59.11,0:12:00.84,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}勇者絕不會死去
Dialogue: 0,0:12:01.40,0:12:05.77,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}為了確認前代勇者乃木園子所言是否屬實
Dialogue: 0,0:12:06.12,0:12:09.31,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}我使用了各種手段尋死
Dialogue: 0,0:12:05.10,0:12:08.38,Screen,,0,0,0,,{\fn華康儷細黑\bord0\b0\fs30\1c&H3F473C&\frx318\fry354\frz28.62\move(478,250,458,-24,0,3253)}切腹
Dialogue: 0,0:12:05.10,0:12:08.38,Screen,,0,0,0,,{\fn華康儷細黑\bord0\b0\fs30\1c&H3F473C&\frx318\fry354\frz28.62\move(528,322,508,60,41,3253)}上吊
Dialogue: 0,0:12:05.10,0:12:08.38,Screen,,0,0,0,,{\fn華康儷細黑\bord0\b0\fs30\1c&H3F473C&\frx318\fry354\frz26.03\move(646,376,626,110,41,3253)}跳樓
Dialogue: 0,0:12:05.10,0:12:08.38,Screen,,0,0,0,,{\fn華康儷細黑\bord0\b0\fs30\1c&H3F473C&\frz21.5\frx320\fry354\move(788,420,776,154,41,3253)}一氧化碳中毒
Dialogue: 0,0:12:05.10,0:12:08.38,Screen,,0,0,0,,{\fn華康儷細黑\bord0\b0\fs30\1c&H3F473C&\frx320\fry354\frz29.6\move(670,552,650,288,41,3253)}淹死
Dialogue: 0,0:12:05.10,0:12:08.38,Screen,,0,0,0,,{\fn華康儷細黑\bord0\b0\fs30\1c&H3F473C&\frx320\fry354\frz29.6\move(706,634,686,366,41,3253)}服毒
Dialogue: 0,0:12:11.02,0:12:13.94,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}無論嘗試何種方法 精靈都成功地阻止了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:14.67,0:12:20.43,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}精靈並不是為了保護勇者 而是為了將勇者永遠束縛在其使命上
Dialogue: 0,0:12:20.80,0:12:24.50,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}也就是說 乃木園子所言屬實
Dialogue: 0,0:12:25.30,0:12:29.23,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}我們的後遺症是盛開這一力量的代價
Dialogue: 0,0:12:30.57,0:12:31.61,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}是供品
Dialogue: 0,0:12:33.12,0:12:38.56,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}那麼 樹就再也無法發出聲音了…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:43.52,0:12:44.82,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}我都不知道
Dialogue: 0,0:12:45.60,0:12:46.90,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}我都不知道
Dialogue: 0,0:12:48.30,0:12:52.43,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}為了保護別人而獻上自己的身軀進行戰鬥
Dialogue: 0,0:12:53.19,0:12:54.32,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}這就是勇者
Dialogue: 0,0:12:56.30,0:13:00.80,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}都怪我把樹拉進勇者社
Dialogue: 0,0:13:01.86,0:13:06.24,InSong-JP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur3}出会えてよかった
Dialogue: 0,0:13:06.90,0:13:13.26,InSong-JP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur3}木漏れ日 眩しい森の中
Dialogue: 0,0:13:13.96,0:13:18.38,InSong-JP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur3}風はいつもあったかくて
Dialogue: 0,0:13:18.38,0:13:25.03,InSong-JP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur3}心ほぐれてく
Dialogue: 0,0:13:26.37,0:13:31.13,InSong-JP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur3}こんな日々がずっと
Dialogue: 0,0:13:31.13,0:13:37.82,InSong-JP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur3}続きますように
Dialogue: 0,0:13:39.02,0:13:46.11,InSong-JP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur3}広がる空は
Dialogue: 0,0:13:46.24,0:13:51.00,InSong-JP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur3}愛や希望で溢れて
Dialogue: 0,0:13:51.00,0:13:57.51,InSong-JP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur3}この声が届くまで
Dialogue: 0,0:13:58.14,0:14:03.90,InSong-JP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur3}歌い続けるから
Dialogue: 0,0:14:04.03,0:14:14.18,InSong-JP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur3}いつも　いつもありがとう
Dialogue: 0,0:14:20.98,0:14:28.11,InSong-JP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur3}この声が届くまで
Dialogue: 0,0:14:28.21,0:14:33.91,InSong-JP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur3}歌い続けるから
Dialogue: 0,0:14:34.03,0:14:44.61,InSong-JP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur3}いつも　いつもありがとう
Dialogue: 0,0:13:01.86,0:13:06.24,InSong-CH,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur3}慶幸與你邂逅於
Dialogue: 0,0:13:06.90,0:13:13.26,InSong-CH,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur3}光斑炫目的林間
Dialogue: 0,0:13:13.96,0:13:18.38,InSong-CH,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur3}風總是那麼溫暖
Dialogue: 0,0:13:18.38,0:13:25.03,InSong-CH,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur3}心靈也隨之解放
Dialogue: 0,0:13:26.37,0:13:31.13,InSong-CH,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur3}但願這樣的日子
Dialogue: 0,0:13:31.13,0:13:37.82,InSong-CH,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur3}永遠地持續下去
Dialogue: 0,0:13:39.02,0:13:46.11,InSong-CH,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur3}如此廣闊的天空
Dialogue: 0,0:13:46.24,0:13:51.00,InSong-CH,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur3}充滿著愛與希望
Dialogue: 0,0:13:51.00,0:13:57.51,InSong-CH,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur3}我會不停地歌唱
Dialogue: 0,0:13:58.14,0:14:03.90,InSong-CH,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur3}直至傳入你心間
Dialogue: 0,0:14:04.03,0:14:14.18,InSong-CH,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur3}一直一直感謝你
Dialogue: 0,0:14:20.98,0:14:28.11,InSong-CH,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur3}我會不停地歌唱
Dialogue: 0,0:14:28.21,0:14:33.91,InSong-CH,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur3}直至傳入你心間
Dialogue: 0,0:14:34.03,0:14:44.61,InSong-CH,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur3}一直一直感謝你
Dialogue: 0,0:13:01.80,0:13:03.32,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}聽我說…姐姐
Dialogue: 0,0:13:03.69,0:13:06.21,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}我有目標了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:06.21,0:13:07.49,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}什麼 什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:13:07.49,0:13:09.76,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}是說有未來的夢想了嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:13:09.86,0:13:11.70,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}那快告訴姐姐吧
Dialogue: 0,0:13:13.17,0:13:14.01,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}保密
Dialogue: 0,0:13:14.65,0:13:15.88,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}好過分
Dialogue: 0,0:13:16.27,0:13:17.96,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}我不會跟別人說的 好嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:13:18.58,0:13:20.08,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}有一天會告訴你的
Dialogue: 0,0:13:27.28,0:13:28.57,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}等等
Dialogue: 0,0:13:32.39,0:13:34.20,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}你要做什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:13:34.30,0:13:36.52,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}我要幹掉大赦
Dialogue: 0,0:13:37.28,0:13:40.21,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}大赦欺騙了我們
Dialogue: 0,0:13:40.80,0:13:44.03,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}盛開的後遺症是治不好的
Dialogue: 0,0:13:47.01,0:13:49.19,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}為什麼非得受這份罪
Dialogue: 0,0:13:50.18,0:13:52.63,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}為什麼非得讓樹失聲
Dialogue: 0,0:13:52.67,0:13:54.79,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}為什麼非得放棄夢想
Dialogue: 0,0:13:54.91,0:13:58.41,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}拯救了世界的代價就是這樣嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:14:00.32,0:14:01.19,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}友奈
Dialogue: 0,0:14:01.37,0:14:02.31,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}讓開
Dialogue: 0,0:14:02.31,0:14:03.14,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}不要
Dialogue: 0,0:14:03.35,0:14:06.78,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}我不想看到風學姐傷害別人的樣子
Dialogue: 0,0:14:06.78,0:14:09.02,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}這種事情怎能饒恕
Dialogue: 0,0:14:10.22,0:14:13.67,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}但是即便是告知我們會有後遺症
Dialogue: 0,0:14:13.95,0:14:16.39,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}我們還是會戰鬥下去的
Dialogue: 0,0:14:17.17,0:14:19.68,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}為了保衛世界只能這樣
Dialogue: 0,0:14:19.73,0:14:22.76,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}沒有人有別的選擇
Dialogue: 0,0:14:25.84,0:14:27.10,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}樹
Dialogue: 0,0:14:35.34,0:14:37.62,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}對不起 大家
Dialogue: 0,0:14:40.47,0:14:46.66,Screen,,0,0,0,,{\fn華康儷中黑\bord0\b0\fs30\rnd8\1c&H294776&\frz1.253\frx356\fry358\move(504,252,240,74,0,4289)}要是沒有與勇者社的大家相遇的話
Dialogue: 0,0:14:40.47,0:14:46.66,Screen,,0,0,0,,{\fn華康儷中黑\bord0\b0\fs30\rnd8\1c&H294776&\frz1.253\frx356\fry358\move(462,370,216,196,35,4289)}一定也不會擁有想歌唱的夢想
Dialogue: 0,0:14:40.47,0:14:46.66,Screen,,0,0,0,,{\fn華康儷中黑\bord0\b0\fs30\rnd8\1c&H294776&\frz1.253\frx356\fry358\move(558,560,312,398,35,4289)}能加入勇者社真是太好了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:47.28,0:14:48.81,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}你冷靜地聽我說
Dialogue: 0,0:14:49.58,0:14:54.55,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}我來告訴你牆壁外側的秘密 這個世界的構成
Dialogue: 0,0:14:55.83,0:14:56.48,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}聽好…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:01.08,0:15:05.55,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}我覺得真相還是由你自己的眼睛來見證比較好
Dialogue: 0,0:15:06.40,0:15:08.59,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}她所說的都是真的
Dialogue: 0,0:15:09.45,0:15:12.81,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}世界在宇宙規模的結界之中
Dialogue: 0,0:15:13.34,0:15:15.69,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}Vertex無限再生
Dialogue: 0,0:15:16.37,0:15:19.64,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}我們一邊奉獻著身體的功能
Dialogue: 0,0:15:19.92,0:15:22.12,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}一邊重複著永無止盡的戰鬥
Dialogue: 0,0:15:22.68,0:15:23.84,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}而最終…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:25.28,0:15:28.38,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}身體就像樹木一樣無法動彈
Dialogue: 0,0:15:28.94,0:15:32.26,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}最終就像這樣被侍奉
Dialogue: 0,0:15:33.23,0:15:38.06,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}我得出的結論是破壞牆壁打倒神樹大人
Dialogue: 0,0:15:38.97,0:15:41.52,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}要從勇者這一祭品中擺脫出來
Dialogue: 0,0:15:41.61,0:15:43.85,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}就只有破壞神樹大人
Dialogue: 0,0:15:44.87,0:15:48.64,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}我無法忍受大家再受到傷害
Dialogue: 0,0:15:53.76,0:15:55.00,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}樹…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:59.50,0:16:02.04,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}為什麼…還要堅持…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:03.09,0:16:04.17,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}謝謝你
Dialogue: 0,0:16:05.13,0:16:08.11,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}不知道為什麼 突然想這麼說
Dialogue: 0,0:16:08.73,0:16:11.63,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}不論是家裡的事還是勇者社的事
Dialogue: 0,0:16:12.35,0:16:15.36,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}把麻煩事都交給姐姐來做
Dialogue: 0,0:16:15.85,0:16:22.00,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}但是 其實我想讓自己能與姐姐並肩前行
Dialogue: 0,0:16:23.17,0:16:24.80,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}何止是並肩
Dialogue: 0,0:16:27.52,0:16:31.81,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}不知不覺間已經走到我前面了呀
Dialogue: 0,0:16:33.21,0:16:35.74,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}為什麼 為什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:16:36.50,0:16:38.28,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}為什麼無法變身
Dialogue: 0,0:16:51.22,0:16:53.57,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}我…我…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:56.24,0:16:59.10,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}不配當…朋友…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:11.16,0:17:12.37,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}夏凜…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:13.95,0:17:14.76,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}友奈
Dialogue: 0,0:17:16.59,0:17:21.61,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}我不再作為大赦的勇者而戰鬥了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:22.92,0:17:27.32,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}從現在開始作為勇者社的一員而戰鬥
Dialogue: 0,0:17:28.96,0:17:32.52,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}我不會讓我們的勇者社遭到毀滅
Dialogue: 0,0:17:34.55,0:17:38.15,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}我不想看到友奈哭泣的樣子
Dialogue: 0,0:17:39.27,0:17:40.37,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}夏凜
Dialogue: 0,0:17:47.11,0:17:48.12,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}真是傻
Dialogue: 0,0:17:48.66,0:17:50.81,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}諸行無常
Dialogue: 0,0:17:51.28,0:17:55.19,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}來吧 好戲從現在開始
Dialogue: 0,0:17:55.46,0:18:01.51,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}遠處的傢伙們聽好了 近處的傢伙們看好了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:01.88,0:18:10.18,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}這就是讚州國中二年級生 勇者社社員三好夏凜的實力
Dialogue: 0,0:18:14.80,0:18:18.56,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}來 吃招吧
Dialogue: 0,0:18:25.60,0:18:30.20,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}在這即將來臨的新世界中 風學姐和樹就不需要再戰鬥了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:31.56,0:18:36.48,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}勇者社五準則 其五
Dialogue: 0,0:18:36.84,0:18:44.30,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}有志者事竟成
Dialogue: 0,0:18:47.29,0:18:48.62,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}夏凜
Dialogue: 0,0:18:49.61,0:18:52.96,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}夏凜也不要再失去什麼了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:53.44,0:18:54.32,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}拜託你了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:56.58,0:19:00.56,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}這個世界 大赦的做法 有多麼淒慘
Dialogue: 0,0:19:01.66,0:19:05.37,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}要拯救我們 就只有這樣
Dialogue: 0,0:19:06.24,0:19:07.66,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}友奈
Dialogue: 0,0:19:09.35,0:19:11.62,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}我想對你說
Dialogue: 0,0:19:12.54,0:19:14.52,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}「謝謝你」
Dialogue: 0,0:19:16.32,0:19:21.81,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}我長期以來一直接受勇者的訓練
Dialogue: 0,0:19:22.33,0:19:26.56,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}只有戰鬥才是我的存在價值
Dialogue: 0,0:19:27.21,0:19:31.41,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}但是多虧了大家 我…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:33.20,0:19:38.21,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}友奈你能夠改變東鄉的內心
Dialogue: 0,0:19:38.76,0:19:39.65,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}一定能夠
Dialogue: 0,0:19:43.82,0:19:45.84,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}停下來
Dialogue: 0,0:19:47.50,0:19:48.64,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}盛開
Dialogue: 0,0:19:49.04,0:19:51.26,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}我曾經作為勇者戰鬥
Dialogue: 0,0:19:51.57,0:19:53.88,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}然後失去了這段記憶
Dialogue: 0,0:19:54.68,0:19:58.67,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}既然我保護不了我最好的朋友 那我就做不成勇者
Dialogue: 0,0:19:59.58,0:20:03.89,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}只要能將一切終結 我們的人間地獄也會結束
Dialogue: 0,0:20:04.83,0:20:07.32,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}與其犧牲友奈和大家
Dialogue: 0,0:20:08.17,0:20:12.16,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}與其再次忘記這珍愛的心意
Dialogue: 0,0:20:13.24,0:20:14.41,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}東鄉同學
Dialogue: 0,0:20:25.30,0:20:26.45,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}我不會忘記
Dialogue: 0,0:20:26.95,0:20:27.90,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}騙人
Dialogue: 0,0:20:28.13,0:20:29.05,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}沒騙人
Dialogue: 0,0:20:30.24,0:20:31.09,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}騙人
Dialogue: 0,0:20:31.42,0:20:32.56,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}沒騙人
Dialogue: 0,0:20:37.69,0:20:38.81,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}真的嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:20:40.84,0:20:42.75,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}我永遠陪伴著你
Dialogue: 0,0:20:43.41,0:20:45.53,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}這樣的話就不會忘記
Dialogue: 0,0:20:46.30,0:20:47.90,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}友奈
Dialogue: 0,0:20:55.81,0:20:56.72,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}怎麼回事
Dialogue: 0,0:20:57.43,0:20:58.43,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}太陽…
Dialogue: 0,0:21:01.70,0:21:03.79,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}我做了這麼過分的事
Dialogue: 0,0:21:03.79,0:21:05.36,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}這不是東鄉同學的錯
Dialogue: 0,0:21:05.73,0:21:06.96,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}我們去阻止它
Dialogue: 0,0:21:07.07,0:21:07.88,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}好
Dialogue: 0,0:21:11.72,0:21:14.20,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}阻止不了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:16.62,0:21:20.45,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}絕對不放棄
Dialogue: 0,0:21:23.78,0:21:24.87,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}友奈
Dialogue: 0,0:21:27.32,0:21:28.93,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}怎麼在這種時候
Dialogue: 0,0:21:31.45,0:21:32.32,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}我的腳…
Dialogue: 0,0:21:36.24,0:21:37.32,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}樹
Dialogue: 0,0:21:38.74,0:21:40.63,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}對不起 在這關鍵的時候
Dialogue: 0,0:21:41.33,0:21:44.29,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}風學姐 我…
Dialogue: 0,0:21:45.68,0:21:47.52,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}歡迎回來 東鄉
Dialogue: 0,0:21:49.95,0:21:53.43,BackGround,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}那裡嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:21:52.03,0:21:52.93,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}夏凜
Dialogue: 0,0:21:53.63,0:21:58.52,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}不要小看勇者社
Dialogue: 0,0:21:59.58,0:22:02.79,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}好 勇者社…
Dialogue: 0,0:22:02.91,0:22:06.69,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}Fight
Dialogue: 0,0:22:23.14,0:22:24.04,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}友奈
Dialogue: 0,0:22:24.23,0:22:24.90,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5\alpha&HA0&}友奈姐
Dialogue: 0,0:22:25.00,0:22:26.05,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}友奈
Dialogue: 0,0:22:26.06,0:22:27.36,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}友奈
Dialogue: 0,0:22:35.51,0:22:39.90,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}擊中吧
Dialogue: 0,0:22:55.17,0:22:58.15,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}勇者社的大家 明明也都很艱辛
Dialogue: 0,0:22:58.48,0:23:02.64,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}但卻為了朋友 拼盡全力 阻止了我
Dialogue: 0,0:23:04.12,0:23:08.59,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}友奈全力衝向了我 全力抱緊了我
Dialogue: 0,0:23:09.73,0:23:12.21,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}所以 我不再害怕
Dialogue: 0,0:23:13.84,0:23:18.39,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}然後我們擊敗了敵人 身體功能也恢復了起來
Dialogue: 0,0:23:19.48,0:23:22.15,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}我重要的回憶 也恢復了過來
Dialogue: 0,0:23:23.47,0:23:26.36,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}雖然還不清楚為什麼會恢復
Dialogue: 0,0:23:26.81,0:23:28.89,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}但至少這不是夢
Dialogue: 0,0:23:29.62,0:23:32.97,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}因為失去的生命 並沒有回來
Dialogue: 0,0:23:35.06,0:23:39.72,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}一起去上學 學習 玩耍 回家
Dialogue: 0,0:23:40.94,0:23:43.68,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}日常竟然是如此珍貴
Dialogue: 0,0:23:44.63,0:23:47.19,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}我很清楚 一切並沒有結束
Dialogue: 0,0:23:47.96,0:23:49.83,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}Vertex還殘存著
Dialogue: 0,0:23:50.44,0:23:53.23,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}不知道未來還會發生什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:23:54.59,0:23:59.63,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}但是現在 我緊緊地擁抱著這無可替代的溫暖
Dialogue: 1,0:22:42.89,0:22:45.20,ED-JP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,100)}さあ　歩き出そう
Dialogue: 1,0:22:45.20,0:22:48.30,ED-JP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,100)}みんなで見た　あの空模様
Dialogue: 1,0:22:48.30,0:22:51.91,ED-JP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,100)}光のカーテン　しめきっても
Dialogue: 1,0:22:51.91,0:22:53.80,ED-JP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,100)}ここは暗くない
Dialogue: 1,0:22:53.80,0:22:55.80,ED-JP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,100)}もう　分かってたの
Dialogue: 1,0:22:55.80,0:22:58.89,ED-JP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,100)}いつか終わる　この瞬間
Dialogue: 1,0:22:58.89,0:23:02.70,ED-JP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,100)}とても大切で　大切で
Dialogue: 1,0:23:02.70,0:23:04.90,ED-JP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,100)}目を背けていた
Dialogue: 1,0:23:05.11,0:23:07.20,ED-JP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,100)}儚い時は
Dialogue: 1,0:23:07.20,0:23:10.09,ED-JP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,100)}あっという間に過ぎて行くよ
Dialogue: 1,0:23:10.09,0:23:12.13,ED-JP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,100)}これは本当に
Dialogue: 1,0:23:12.13,0:23:15.30,ED-JP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,100)}起こった出来事？
Dialogue: 1,0:23:15.30,0:23:17.88,ED-JP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,100)}そのカケラを夕陽に
Dialogue: 1,0:23:17.88,0:23:20.67,ED-JP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,100)}かざして確かめてみるよ
Dialogue: 1,0:23:20.67,0:23:22.88,ED-JP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,100)}忘れられない
Dialogue: 1,0:23:22.88,0:23:25.64,ED-JP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,100)}忘れちゃいけない
Dialogue: 1,0:23:25.64,0:23:32.67,ED-JP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,100)}ひとつひとつが素晴らしい思い出
Dialogue: 1,0:23:32.67,0:23:37.08,ED-JP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,100)}いつでも　目に浮かぶその笑顔
Dialogue: 1,0:23:37.20,0:23:43.60,ED-JP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,100)}ひとつひとつが奇跡なんだ
Dialogue: 1,0:23:43.60,0:23:49.71,ED-JP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,100)}ここにこうして舞い降りてきたの
Dialogue: 1,0:23:49.94,0:23:55.53,ED-JP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,100)}So bright
Dialogue: 1,0:22:42.89,0:22:45.20,ED-CH,,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,100)}來　邁開腳步吧
Dialogue: 1,0:22:45.20,0:22:48.30,ED-CH,,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,100)}大家看到的天空
Dialogue: 1,0:22:48.30,0:22:51.91,ED-CH,,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,100)}即便拉上光之簾
Dialogue: 1,0:22:51.91,0:22:53.80,ED-CH,,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,100)}這裡也並不黑暗
Dialogue: 1,0:22:53.80,0:22:55.80,ED-CH,,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,100)}我現在已經明白
Dialogue: 1,0:22:55.80,0:22:58.89,ED-CH,,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,100)}這瞬間終將結束
Dialogue: 1,0:22:58.89,0:23:02.70,ED-CH,,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,100)}這是那麼的寶貴
Dialogue: 1,0:23:02.70,0:23:04.90,ED-CH,,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,100)}我不禁避開視線
Dialogue: 1,0:23:05.11,0:23:07.20,ED-CH,,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,100)}夢幻般的時刻
Dialogue: 1,0:23:07.20,0:23:10.09,ED-CH,,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,100)}真是轉瞬即逝
Dialogue: 1,0:23:10.09,0:23:12.13,ED-CH,,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,100)}這是真真正正
Dialogue: 1,0:23:12.13,0:23:15.30,ED-CH,,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,100)}發生過的事嗎
Dialogue: 1,0:23:15.30,0:23:17.88,ED-CH,,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,100)}殘片對著夕陽
Dialogue: 1,0:23:17.88,0:23:20.67,ED-CH,,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,100)}來試著確認吧
Dialogue: 1,0:23:20.67,0:23:22.88,ED-CH,,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,100)}這些無法忘卻
Dialogue: 1,0:23:22.88,0:23:25.64,ED-CH,,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,100)}這些不能忘卻
Dialogue: 1,0:23:25.64,0:23:32.67,ED-CH,,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,100)}每每都是美妙回憶
Dialogue: 1,0:23:32.67,0:23:37.08,ED-CH,,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,100)}總是回想起那笑容
Dialogue: 1,0:23:37.20,0:23:43.60,ED-CH,,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,100)}每每都是一份奇蹟
Dialogue: 1,0:23:43.60,0:23:49.71,ED-CH,,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,100)}就像這樣降臨於此
Dialogue: 1,0:23:49.94,0:23:55.53,ED-CH,,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,100)}So bright
